10 REM *** SPRITE MOVER ***
20 PRINT CHR$(147)
30 V = 53248 : REM VIC-II BASE
40 X = 100 : Y = 100

100 REM *** SETUP SPRITE ***
110 POKE 2040, 13 : REM POINTER TO BLOCK 13
120 FOR I = 832 TO 894 : POKE I, 255 : NEXT : REM SOLID BLOCK
130 POKE V+21, 1 : REM ENABLE SPRITE 0
140 POKE V+39, 7 : REM YELLOW COLOR

200 REM *** MAIN LOOP ***
210 POKE V, X   : REM SET X
220 POKE V+1, Y : REM SET Y
230 GET K$
240 IF K$ = "" THEN GOTO 230
250 IF K$ = "W" THEN Y = Y - 5
260 IF K$ = "S" THEN Y = Y + 5
270 IF K$ = "A" THEN X = X - 5
280 IF K$ = "D" THEN X = X + 5
290 REM BOUNDARY CHECKS
300 IF X < 0 THEN X = 0
310 IF X > 255 THEN X = 255
320 IF Y < 50 THEN Y = 50
330 IF Y > 250 THEN Y = 250
340 GOTO 200
